  "texts": [
    "It can capture event type information in the text and make the model more sensitive to implicit trigger words.",
    "(3) The recall of our method on Tri-CLS is slightly lower than GTEE-DYNPREF in Table 2, but the precision is far higher than it.",
    "It shows that GTEE-DYNPREF integrating context information with type-specific prefixes captures more events.",
